### Konko AI Agent - REST API Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client or IntelliJ HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000


### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### Root Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/


### OpenAPI Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json


### ============================================
### Conversation Endpoints
### ============================================

### Start a New Conversation
# @name startConversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations
Content-Type: application/json


### Get Conversation State
# Replace {session_id} with actual session ID from startConversation response
@sessionId = {{startConversation.response.body.session_id}}

GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations/{{sessionId}}


### Send Message to Conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations/{{sessionId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": "My name is John Doe"
}


### Send Another Message (Email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations/{{sessionId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": "My email is john@example.com"
}


### Delete Conversation
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/conversations/{{sessionId}}


### ============================================
### Manual Testing with Fixed Session ID
### ============================================

### Start Conversation (Manual)
# @name manualStart
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations
Content-Type: application/json


### Send Message (Manual) - Replace session_id below
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations/REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": "Hello, my name is Luis"
}


### Get Conversation (Manual) - Replace session_id below
GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations/REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID
